{"tid":900170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府跨部門開會 跟進內地邊防部隊「跨境倒垃圾」","createTime":"2018-11-13T04:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T04:39:58.000Z","uid":150685,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b1a47dd30c8f33feb6e8fcd90deab02e6aa6935b","tid":900170,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T04:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181112/large/1542034119_4bab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181112%2Flarge%2F1542034119_4bab.png&h=c9203887&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《傳真社》日前揭發，有身穿迷彩服的深圳邊防部隊人員，涉擅自越過深圳河到沙頭角一處土地，傾倒垃圾廢物。<br />\n<br />\n政府今晚發稿回應有關報道，指特區政府關注有關事宜，政務司司長張建宗今午主持了跨部門會議，與發展局、保安局、政制及內地事務局等部門進行會面。<br />\n<br />\n地政總署及警務處等部門，今天進行了實地視察，並正翻查過往地界記錄、航拍照片及工程記錄等，以釐清事實。<br />\n<br />\n政府表示，特區政府相關政策局及部門，將繼續積極跟進，以期盡快核實及交代有關情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181112/58905887?fbclid=IwAR3a2lZuHDlQqvrz_hI-EgMJc5kSXZgNCQpFzAhQdHWdwx6cMiaiLxrNHUY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181112%2F58905887%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3a2lZuHDlQqvrz_hI-EgMJc5kSXZgNCQpFzAhQdHWdwx6cMiaiLxrNHUY&d=FOSiJIdA3EVv5kz%2FnXbgJQCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=acfa8d61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181112%2F58905887%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3a2lZuHDlQqvrz_hI-EgMJc5kSXZgNCQpFzAhQdHWdwx6cMiaiLxrNHUY&h=4d386984\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181112/58905887?fbclid=IwAR3a2lZuHDlQqvrz_hI-EgMJc5kSXZgNCQpFzAhQdHWdwx6cMiaiLxrNHUY</a>"},{"pid":"f30f1a2427cb903f42f8ab4109efc0901aafd5b2","tid":900170,"uid":28387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T04:36:55.000Z","msg":"睇下班（官）點解話啦今次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391c6af8a79e1780744287cf7b10f493e60a38bb","tid":900170,"uid":171192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T04:39:58.000Z","msg":"政府：沒事兒 沒事兒"}]}